            "title": "Intro",
            "id": 80266,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A veces las funciones necesitan información específica para ayudarlas a realizar sus tareas. Como una función que agrega el nombre de un jugador a un equipo.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;html&gt;&#xA; &lt;head&gt;&#xA;  &lt;style&gt;&#xA;   body {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;    height: 350px;&#xA;    font-size: 16px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    background-color: #F0F8FF&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   button {&#xA;    width: 200px;&#xA;    height: 30px;&#xA;    font-size: 20px;&#xA;    border-radius: 5px;&#xA;    margin: 0 auto;&#xA;    display: block;&#xA;    color: black;&#xA;    outline: none;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   h2 {&#xA;    text-align: center;&#xA;   }&#xA;   &#xA;   #playerList {&#xA;    text-align: left;&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/style&gt;&#xA; &lt;/head&gt;&#xA; &lt;body id=&quot;main&quot;&gt;&#xA;  &lt;h1&gt;Add Team Players&lt;/h1&gt;&#xA;  &lt;div class=&quot;Signup&quot;&gt;&#xA;   &lt;div class=&quot;playerInput&quot;&gt;&#xA;    &lt;input id=&quot;pInput&quot; type=&quot;text&quot;&#xA;     placeholder=&quot;Enter a player name&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&#xA;   &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;   &lt;button onClick=&quot;add()&quot;&gt;Submit&lt;/button&gt;&#xA;   &lt;h3&gt;Current Team&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/div&gt;&#xA;  &lt;ul id=playerList&gt;&#xA;  &lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;  &lt;p id=&quot;full&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;  &lt;script&gt;&#xA;   let number = 0;&#xA;   &#xA;   function add() {&#xA;    if (number &gt;= 3) {&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;full&quot;).innerHTML = &quot;Team Full&quot;;&#xA;    } else {&#xA;     const player = document.getElementById(&quot;pInput&quot;).value;&#xA;     const node = document.createElement(&quot;P&quot;);&#xA;     const textnode = document.createTextNode(&quot;Added: &quot; + player);&#xA;     node.appendChild(textnode);&#xA;     document.getElementById(&quot;playerList&quot;).appendChild(node);&#xA;     number++;&#xA;    }&#xA;   }&#xA;  &lt;/script&gt;&#xA; &lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Variables in functions",
            "id": 80268,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para empezar, podemos usar variables dentro de funciones. Como crear <code>name = \"Ron\"</code> y usarlo en la declaración de visualización.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_ron\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Ron&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hello, \" /><text value=\"{name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet_ron()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"19\" endIndex=\"23\" /><option startIndex=\"24\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"31\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello, Ron\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>name</code> seguido de <code>=</code> y finalmente <code>\"Ron\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Similar code",
            "id": 80276,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Cómo saludaríamos a otra persona? Podríamos crear y llamar a una nueva función <code>greet_leslie()</code> con un código similar.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_ron\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Ron&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hello, \" /><text value=\"{name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet_ron()\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet_leslie\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"()\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  name = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Leslie&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hello, \" /><text value=\"{name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet_leslie()\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"74\" endIndex=\"88\" /><option startIndex=\"134\" endIndex=\"146\" /><option startIndex=\"146\" endIndex=\"147\" /><option startIndex=\"147\" endIndex=\"148\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello, Ron\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hello, Leslie\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>greet_leslie()</code> seguido de <code>greet_leslie</code> y luego <code>(</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Passing",
            "id": 80269,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>En lugar de escribir dos funciones, podemos pasar información específica como <code>\"Leslie\"</code> a solo una función, sin repetir código.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(name)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hello, \" /><text value=\"{name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet(\" /><text value=\"&quot;April&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"greet(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Leslie&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"64\" endIndex=\"72\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello, April\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"Hello, Leslie\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>\"Leslie\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parameter",
            "id": 80270,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para pasar un valor a una función, primero añadimos una variable llamada <strong>parámetro</strong> dentro de los paréntesis de la función. Aquí, pasaremos <code>name</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(name)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"14\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>name</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Parameter",
            "id": 80271,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>El parámetro, aquí <code>name</code>, actúa como una variable que almacena un valor. Sin embargo, aún no tiene un valor dentro.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"greet\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(name)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  print(\" /><text value=\"f&quot;Hello, \" /><text value=\"{name}\" class=\"subst\" /><text value=\"&quot;\" /><text value=\")\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"14\" /><option startIndex=\"35\" endIndex=\"39\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>name</code> seguido de <code>name</code>.</p></body></html>"
